      <p>This creature has the body of a large <a href="ch73s15.html#MonstersAnimals48">dog</a>, with a smooth black coat and a mouth full of sharp teeth.<a href="img/MonstersS.Shadow_Mastiff.jpg" target="_blank"><span class="inlinemediaobject"><img src="thumb/MonstersS.Shadow_Mastiff.jpg" align="right"/></span></a></p>
      <p>A <a href="ch71s06.html#MonstersS39">shadow mastiff</a> is slightly more than 2 feet high at the shoulder and weighs about 200 pounds.</p>
      <p><a href="ch71s06.html#MonstersS39">Shadow mastiffs</a> cannot speak, but they understand Common.</p>
      <div class="sect4" lang="en">
        <div class="titlepage">
          <div>
            <div>
              <h5 class="title"><a name="id2170605"/>Combat</h5>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="keywordset" style="display:none">
          <div class="keyword">monsterinfo</div>
        </div>
        <a class="indexterm" name="MonstersS40"/>
        <p><a href="ch71s06.html#MonstersS39">Shadow mastiffs</a> prefer fighting in <a href="ch71s05.html#MonstersS31">shadows</a> or dark conditions, which gives them a great advantage.</p>
        <p>If a magical light source negates the <a href="ch71s05.html#MonstersS31">shadows</a> around them, <a href="ch71s06.html#MonstersS39">shadow mastiffs</a> are cunning enough to either move out of the light or back off and break up the opposition with their baying. They have been known to seize and carry off items enspelled with <span class="emphasis"><em><a href="ch45.html#SpellsD-E5">daylight</a></em></span> spells.</p>
        <div class="simplesect" lang="en">
          <div class="titlepage"/>
          <a name="id2171499"/>
          <div class="keywordset" style="display:none">
            <div class="keyword">other</div>
          </div>
          <a class="indexterm" name="MonstersS41"/>
          <p><span class="strong"><strong>Bay (Su):</strong></span> When a <a href="ch71s06.html#MonstersS39">shadow mastiff</a> howls or barks, all creatures except evil outsiders within a 300-foot spread must succeed on a DC 13 Will save or become panicked for 2d4 rounds. This is a sonic mind-affecting fear effect. Whether or not the save is successful, an affected creature is immune to the same mastiff's bay for 24 hours. The save DC is Charisma-based.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="simplesect" lang="en">
          <div class="titlepage"/>
          <a name="id2171542"/>
          <div class="keywordset" style="display:none">
            <div class="keyword">other</div>
          </div>
          <a class="indexterm" name="MonstersS42"/>
          <p><span class="strong"><strong>Trip (Ex):</strong></span> A <a href="ch71s06.html#MonstersS39">shadow mastiff</a> that hits with its bite attack can attempt to trip the opponent as a free action (+3 check modifier) without making a touch attack or provoking an attack of opportunity. If the attempt fails, the opponent cannot react to trip the <a href="ch71s06.html#MonstersS39">shadow mastiff</a>.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="simplesect" lang="en">
          <div class="titlepage"/>
          <a name="id2171593"/>
          <div class="keywordset" style="display:none">
            <div class="keyword">other</div>
          </div>
          <a class="indexterm" name="MonstersS43"/>
          <p><span class="strong"><strong>Shadow Blend (Su):</strong></span> In any condition of illumination other than full daylight, a <a href="ch71s06.html#MonstersS39">shadow mastiff</a> can disappear into the <a href="ch71s05.html#MonstersS31">shadows</a>, giving it total concealment. Artificial illumination, even a <span class="emphasis"><em><a href="ch47.html#SpellsH-L67">light</a></em></span> or <span class="emphasis"><em><a href="ch44.html#SpellsC40">continual flame</a></em></span> spell, does not negate this ability. A <span class="emphasis"><em><a href="ch45.html#SpellsD-E5">daylight</a></em></span> spell, however, will.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="simplesect" lang="en">
          <div class="titlepage"/>
          <a name="id2171674"/>
          <div class="keywordset" style="display:none">
            <div class="keyword">other</div>
          </div>
          <a class="indexterm" name="MonstersS44"/>
          <p><span class="strong"><strong>Skills:</strong></span> *A <a href="ch71s06.html#MonstersS39">shadow mastiff</a> has a +4 racial bonus on <a href="ch16s03.html#CombinedSkills303">Survival</a> checks when tracking by scent.</p>
